Class ApiUserContextBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.apitransport.ApiUserContextBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ARServerUser

    public abstract class ApiUserContextBase
extends Object
implements ApiUserContextI
    This is the abstract base class for ARServerUser and CMDB API calls entry point i.e. public class ARServerUser extends ApiUserContextBase implements ApiUserContextI
